WebSchedulr — Split Panel Layout Engineering Prompt

What You Are Building
Replace the current single-pane calendar with a persistent split layout: left 62% is the scrollable calendar pane (all four views), right 38% is a fixed contextual panel that never scrolls away and always shows provider load and available slots.
The prototype is at webschedulr-split.html. Every interaction, component, and data shape in this prompt maps directly to that file. Read it before writing any code.

